b'[<p><i><b>UFC Fight Night: Shogun vs. Saint Preux</b></i> (also known as <i><b>UFC Fight Night 56</b></i>) was a <a href="/wiki/Mixed_martial_arts" title="Mixed martial arts">mixed martial arts</a> event held at the <a href="/wiki/Gin%C3%A1sio_Municipal_Tancredo_Neves" title="Gin\xc3\xa1sio Municipal Tancredo Neves">Gin\xc3\xa1sio Municipal Tancredo Neves</a> in <a href="/wiki/Uberl%C3%A2ndia" title="Uberl\xc3\xa2ndia">Uberl\xc3\xa2ndia</a>, <a href="/wiki/Brazil" title="Brazil">Brazil</a>, on November 8, 2014.<sup class="reference" id="cite_ref-FNUberl\xc3\xa2ndia_2-0"><a href="#cite_note-FNUberl\xc3\xa2ndia-2">[2]</a></sup>\n</p>, <p>After previously holding events in <a href="/wiki/Minas_Gerais" title="Minas Gerais">Minas Gerais</a>\'s largest city <a href="/wiki/Belo_Horizonte" title="Belo Horizonte">Belo Horizonte</a>, the event was the first that the organization has hosted in Uberl\xc3\xa2ndia.<sup class="reference" id="cite_ref-FNUberl\xc3\xa2ndia_2-1"><a href="#cite_note-FNUberl\xc3\xa2ndia-2">[2]</a></sup>\n</p>, <p>A light heavyweight bout between <a href="/wiki/Maur%C3%ADcio_Rua" title="Maur\xc3\xadcio Rua">Maur\xc3\xadcio Rua</a> and <a href="/wiki/Jimi_Manuwa" title="Jimi Manuwa">Jimi Manuwa</a> was expected to serve as event headliner.<sup class="reference" id="cite_ref-UberlandiaME_3-0"><a href="#cite_note-UberlandiaME-3">[3]</a></sup> However, on October 29, it was announced that Manuwa had pulled out of the fight due to injury and <a href="/wiki/Ovince_Saint_Preux" title="Ovince Saint Preux">Ovince Saint Preux</a> replaced him in main event against Rua.<sup class="reference" id="cite_ref-Staff_4-0"><a href="#cite_note-Staff-4">[4]</a></sup>\n</p>, <p><a href="/wiki/Rafael_Cavalcante" title="Rafael Cavalcante">Rafael Cavalcante</a> was expected to face <a href="/wiki/Ovince_Saint_Preux" title="Ovince Saint Preux">Ovince Saint Preux</a> at the event.  However, Cavalcante pulled out of the bout citing injury and was replaced by <a href="/wiki/Francimar_Barroso" title="Francimar Barroso">Francimar Barroso</a>.<sup class="reference" id="cite_ref-FeijaoOut_5-0"><a href="#cite_note-FeijaoOut-5">[5]</a></sup> Subsequently, this fight was cancelled when Saint Preux was chosen as an injury replacement in the event headliner.<sup class="reference" id="cite_ref-Staff_4-1"><a href="#cite_note-Staff-4">[4]</a></sup>\n</p>, <p><a href="/wiki/Dhiego_Lima" title="Dhiego Lima">Dhiego Lima</a> was originally scheduled to face <a href="/wiki/Pawel_Pawlak" title="Pawel Pawlak">Pawel Pawlak</a> at this event.  However, Pawlak was forced to pull out of the fight due to injury and was replaced by promotional newcomer Jorge de Oliveira.<sup class="reference" id="cite_ref-6"><a href="#cite_note-6">[6]</a></sup>\n</p>, <p>A bout between <a href="/wiki/Ian_McCall_(fighter)" title="Ian McCall (fighter)">Ian McCall</a> and <a href="/wiki/John_Lineker" title="John Lineker">John Lineker</a> was expected to be the co-main event.  However, just hours after both fighters successfully made weight, it was announced that McCall had to pull out of the fight due to a viral infection and the bout was pulled from the event entirely. The bout between Dhiego Lima and Jorge de Oliveira was moved to the main card.<sup class="reference" id="cite_ref-7"><a href="#cite_note-7">[7]</a></sup>\n</p>, <p><sup class="reference" id="cite_ref-8"><a href="#cite_note-8">[8]</a></sup>\n</p>, <p>The following fighters were awarded $50,000 bonuses:<sup class="reference" id="cite_ref-9"><a href="#cite_note-9">[9]</a></sup>\n</p>, <p><br/>\n</p>]'